OL,3,CCost of explosion investigation
OL,4,Cexceeds #11 million
OL,6,FThe cost of the police investigation
OL,7,Finto the Haut du Mont explosion in
OL,8,FJersey has exceeded #11 million, new
OL,9,Ffigures have revealed.
OL,11,FIt is one of the biggest undertakings
OL,12,Fin the history of Jersey's police
OL,13,Fforce, after ten people died as a
OL,14,Fresult of the explosion in December
OL,15,F2022.
OL,17,FMore than 800 lines of enquiry are
OL,18,Fbeing investigated, and police have
OL,19,Ftaken over 300 statements and
OL,20,Fcollected more than 600 exhibits.
