OL,3,CCost of explosion investigation
OL,4,Cexceeds #11 million
OL,6,FTravel and accommodation costs for
OL,7,Fforensic experts coming to the island
OL,8,Fare among the outstanding expenses.
OL,10,FWith #11,688,000 the total cost to
OL,11,Fdate (as of 31 August 2024), just
OL,12,Funder #1.9 million remains in the
OL,13,Fallocated budget for the remainder of
OL,14,Fthe year.
OL,16,FThe cause of the tragedy is yet to be
OL,17,Fconfirmed but police say their working
OL,18,Fhypothesis is a gas explosion.
