OL,6,FThe figures were released in response
OL,7,Fto a written question to Treasury
OL,8,FMinister Elaine Minister by Deputy
OL,9,FSteve Ahier.
OL,11,FThey were given alongside the cost of
OL,12,Fthe L'Ecume II investigation - which
OL,13,Fhas cost #2,889,000 to date with
OL,14,F#798,000 remaining in the 2024 budget.
